Package: nhlutils
Type: Package
Title: Utilities for working with NHL data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person( "Sai", "Okabayashi", email = "sokabayashi@newjerseydevils.com",
  role = c( "aut", "cre" ) ) )
Author: Sai Okabayashi [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Sai Okabayashi <sokabayashi@newjerseydevils.com>
Description: Commonly used functions for working with NHL data in the NJD
    environment. This includes conversion functions for clock time, aggregation
    functions for player stats.
